[00:28:54.800 --> 00:28:57.800]  Emmanuel。
[00:28:57.800 --> 00:28:59.800]  繼續唱,
[00:28:59.800 --> 00:29:03.800]  Emmanuel,
[00:29:03.800 --> 00:29:08.800]  神與你同在,
[00:29:08.800 --> 00:29:13.800]  Emmanuel,
